Package: hireLetter
Type: Package
Title: General Customizable Accpetance or Rejection Letter Templates
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author@R: "Ramya Subramanian <rsubramanian23@usf.edu> [aut,cre]"
Description: This package holds functions for individuals on a hiring committee to send
    acceptance or rejection letters based on qualifications they set. The default qualifications
    available in the hire function are age, GPA, and work experience. The letter template is 
    created using a S4 class.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: CC0
LazyData: true
